Package example.data

Class StaticUserDAO

java.lang.Object
example.data.StaticUserDAO
All Implemented Interfaces:
UserDAO
public class StaticUserDAO extends Object implements UserDAO
Provides basic CRUD functionality needed by a data access object to store and retrieve information about a User. This implementation uses a static database connection.
